DiagramForge — canvas-based cloud architecture diagram editor.
Static site: plain ES modules + Web Components, no build. Lint with `npm run lint`.
Code style: leading-comma/leading-semicolon layout, tabs, `$`/`_` shorthand. Match surrounding code.

Diagrams are plain JSON files (`.cde`). To add/modify/arrange nodes and links, edit the `.cde`
file directly — there is no in-app AI console. Read **SCHEMA.md** for the format; **AUTO.md**
(AI contract + MCP ops) and **USAGE.md** (dev server / MCP setup) for live editing.
Sample files are in Samples/.
